| title = Photochemical Preparation of Xenon Difluoride" Photochemical Preparation of Xenon Difluoride
|author1=Weeks, J. |author2=Matheson, M. |author3=Chernick, C. | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]
| volume = 84
| issue = 23
| pages = 4612–4613
| year = 1962
| doi = 10.1021/ja00882a063 }}</ref>  Williamson 报道说，该反应在干燥的[[派热克斯玻璃|派热克斯玻璃]]灯泡中，标准大气压下，以太阳光为紫外线源，反应过程同样良好。他注意到即使在阴天，也可以进行二氟化氙的合成。 <ref>{{cite book | last1 = Williamson | first1 = Stanley M. | last2 = Sladky | first2 = Friedrich O. | last3 = Bartlett | first3 = Neil | title = Xenon Difluoride | journal = [[Inorg._Synth.|Inorg. Synth.]] | volume = 11 | pages = 147–151 | year = 1968 | doi = 10.1002/9780470132425.ch31| series = Inorganic Syntheses | isbn = 9780470132425 }}</ref>

在先前的合成中，会有纯化氟气以除去[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]的步骤。 Šmalc和Lutar发现，如果跳过此步骤，反应速率将以原始速率的四倍进行。 <ref>{{cite book | last1 = Šmalc | first1 = Andrej | last2 = Lutar | first2 = Karel | last3 = Kinkead | first3 = Scott A. | title = Xenon Difluoride (Modification) | doi = 10.1002/9780470132609.ch1 | journal = [[Inorg._Synth.|Inorg. Synth.]] | year = 1992 | pages = 1–4 | volume = 29| series = Inorganic Syntheses | isbn = 9780470132609 }}</ref>

